fields.description:
On a fresh cloud setup, first action I took was registering paravirt kern/ramdisk/image and attempted to run it. As the paravirt image would need to be converted the imaging worker process went into action. I happened to be watching cloud-output log as it all happened and this really outrageous explosion happened. The worker image launched successfully and conversion and run of the paravirt image was successful as well.
